## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology | Why |
|-------|-----------|-----|
| **Frontend** | HTML/CSS/JS + Chart.js (heatmap) | Fast to build, no framework overhead |
| **Backend** | Python FastAPI | Best PDF parsing ecosystem (pdfplumber, PyPDF2), native OpenAI SDK |
| **AI Layer** | OpenAI GPT-4 + text-embedding-3-small | Stylometry, citation analysis, semantic search |
| **PDF Parsing** | `pdfplumber` (primary) + `PyPDF2` (fallback) | Most reliable PDF text extraction |
| **NLP Helpers** | `nltk` or `spacy` (lightweight) | Sentence tokenization, basic NLP metrics |
| **Arxiv Search** | `arxiv` Python package (free API) | Search arxiv papers by query/embedding |
| **Visualization** | D3.js or custom CSS heatmap | Paragraph-level authorship heatmap |
| **Database** | SQLite (if needed) or in-memory | Cache analysis results during session |
| **Deployment** | Vercel (frontend) + Railway/Render (backend) | Quick, free |

